    "headline": "Team Topologies adopted \u2014 intentional design begins",
    "body": "For the first time, Finch maps its teams using a formal framework (Team Topologies). Stream-aligned, Platform, Enabling, and Complicated Subsystem designations are assigned. Seven new hires join, mostly at IC1\u2013IC2 level, many remote. The structural problems aren't fixed yet, but they're now named and mapped. Adrienne begins drafting the Q1 2026 workforce assessment.",
